---
title: Veggie Gyoza & Beef Katsu Curry Sauce with Corn Rice & Coriander
description: Who says comfort food can’t be exciting? Golden veggie gyoza take a delicious dive into a pool of rich, velvety katsu curry sauce. Paired with fluffy corn-studded rice and a sprinkle of fresh coriander, this dish is a flavour-packed hug in a bowl. Ready your chopsticks—it’s time to dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
